yle=\"font-family:\r\n\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" inherit\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Nutzer\r\nwerden aufgefordert, dieses Dokument sorgfältig zur Kenntnis zu nehmen.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" inherit\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Diese\r\nAnwendung wird angeboten von:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">HUFCHECK\r\nBernd Jung<br>\r\nAm Erdbeerenberg 11<br>\r\nD-65614 Beselich<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">E-Mail-Adresse\r\ndes Anbieters:</span></b><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\r\n\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">&nbsp;hufcheck@hufschuhberatung.online<o:p></o:p></span></p><div class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-align:center\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de;mso-no-proof:yes\"=\"\">\r\n\r\n<hr size=\"0\" width=\"99%\" noshade=\"\" style=\"color:#666666\" align=\"center\">\r\n\r\n</span></div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:18.0pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#141414;=\"\" mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">NUTZUNGSBEDINGUNGEN<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:18.0pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#141414;=\"\" mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Sofern\r\nnicht anders angegeben, gelten bei dem Zugriff auf diese Anwendung die in\r\ndiesem Abschnitt aufgeführten Bedingungen.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Einzelne\r\noder zusätzliche Nutzungs- oder Zugriffsbedingungen können unter bestimmten\r\nUmständen anwendbar sein und werden in solchen Fällen in diesem Dokument\r\nausdrücklich benannt.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Durch\r\nNutzen des Dienstes bestätigen Nutzer, die folgenden Bedingungen zu erfüllen:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:#444444;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Über diese Anwendung verfügbare Inhalte<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Sofern\r\nnicht anders angegeben oder deutlich erkennbar, sind alle über diese Anwendung\r\nverfügbaren Inhalte Eigentum des Anbieters und werden vom Anbieter oder seinen\r\nLizenzgebern bereitgestellt.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Der\r\nAnbieter unternimmt alle Anstrengungen, um auszuschließen, dass die über diese\r\nAnwendung bereitgestellten Inhalte gegen geltende Rechtsvorschriften oder\r\nRechte Dritter verstoßen. Es ist jedoch nicht immer möglich, dieses Ergebnis zu\r\nerreichen.<br>\r\nIn solchen Fällen sind Nutzer gebeten, ihre Beschwerde vorzugsweise an die in\r\ndiesem Dokument angegebenen Kontaktdaten zu richten. Das Recht, etwaige\r\nAnsprüche (außer)gerichtlich durchzusetzen, bleibt hiervon unberührt.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:#444444;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Zugriff auf externe Ressourcen<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Nutzer\r\nkönnen u. U. über diese Anwendung auf externe Ressourcen zugreifen, die von\r\nDritten bereitgestellt werden. Die Nutzer erkennen an und akzeptieren, dass der\r\nAnbieter keine Kontrolle über solche Ressourcen hat und daher nicht für deren\r\nInhalt und Verfügbarkeit verantwortlich ist.<br>\r\nDie Bedingungen, unter denen solche von Dritten bereitgestellten Ressourcen zur\r\nVerfügung stehen und unter denen Nutzungsrechte an solchen Inhalten ggf.\r\neingeräumt werden, ergeben sich aus den vertraglichen Bestimmungen jedes\r\nDritten oder, hilfsweise, aus den jeweils anwendbaren gesetzlichen\r\nVorschriften.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:#444444;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Zulässige Nutzung<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Diese\r\nAnwendung und der Dienst dürfen nur bestimmungsgemäß und entsprechend diesen\r\nAGB sowie entsprechend den jeweils anwendbaren gesetzlichen Vorschriften\r\ngenutzt werden.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Nutzer\r\nsind selbst dafür verantwortlich, dass ihr Zugriff auf diese Anwendung und/oder\r\nihre Nutzung des Dienstes keine gesetzlichen Vorschriften, Verordnungen oder\r\nRechte Dritter verletzt.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:18.0pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#141414;=\"\" mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Gemeinsame Bestimmungen<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:18.0pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#141414;=\"\" mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:#444444;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Keine Verzichtserklärung<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Unterlässt\r\nes der Anbieter, ein Recht aus diesen AGB geltend zu machen oder eine\r\nBestimmung aus diesen AGB durchzusetzen, stellt dies keinen Verzicht auf ein\r\nsolches Recht oder eine solche Bestimmung dar. Kein Verzicht gilt als weiterer\r\noder anhaltender Verzicht.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:#444444;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Serviceunterbrechung<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Um\r\neinen bestmöglichen Service zu gewährleisten, behält sich der Anbieter das\r\nRecht vor, den Dienst für Wartungen, Systemaktualisierungen oder andere\r\nÄnderungen zu unterbrechen. Er wird die Nutzer angemessen informieren.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Im\r\nRahmen der gesetzlichen Bestimmungen kann der Anbieter auch beschließen, den\r\nDienst ganz auszusetzen oder zu beenden. Im Fall der Beendigung des Dienstes\r\nwird der Anbieter mit den Nutzern zusammenarbeiten, um es ihnen zu ermöglichen,\r\npersonenbezogene Daten oder Informationen gemäß dem jeweils geltenden Recht zu\r\nlöschen.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Darüber\r\nhinaus kann es vorkommen, dass der Dienst aus Gründen, die nicht in der\r\nKontrolle des Anbieters liegen, wie „höhere Gewalt“, nicht verfügbar ist (z.B.\r\nArbeitskampfmaßnahmen, Infrastrukturausfälle oder Stromausfälle usw.).<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:#444444;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Weiterveräußerung<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Nutzer\r\ndürfen ohne die ausdrückliche vorherige schriftliche Genehmigung des Anbieters,\r\ndie entweder direkt oder über ein rechtmäßiges Reseller-Programm gewährt wird,\r\ndiese Anwendung und den Dienst in keiner Art reproduzieren, duplizieren,\r\nkopieren, verkaufen, weiterverkaufen oder ausschöpfen.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:#444444;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Geistige Eigentumsrechte<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Unbeschadet\r\nkonkreterer Bestimmungen dieser AGB, sind alle geistigen Eigentumsrechte, wie\r\nUrheberrechte, Markenrechte, Patentrechte und Designrechte im Zusammenhang mit\r\ndem Dienst (diese Anwendung) ausschließliches Eigentum des Anbieters oder\r\nseiner Lizenzgeber und unterliegen dem Schutz des jeweils anwendbaren Rechts\r\noder internationaler Verträge in Bezug auf geistiges Eigentum.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Alle\r\nMarken-, Namens- oder Bildmarken – und alle anderen Marken, Handelsnamen,\r\nDienstleistungsmarken, Wortmarken, Illustrationen, Bilder oder Logos – die im\r\nZusammenhang mit dem Dienst (diese Anwendung) erscheinen, sind und bleiben\r\nausschließliches Eigentum des Anbieters oder seiner Lizenzgeber und unterliegen\r\ndem Schutz anwendbaren Rechts oder internationaler Verträge in Bezug auf\r\ngeistiges Eigentum.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:#444444;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Änderungen dieser AGB<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Der\r\nAnbieter behält sich das Recht vor, diese AGB jederzeit zu ändern oder\r\nanderweitig zu modifizieren. In diesem Fall wird der Anbieter den Nutzer\r\nangemessen über diese Änderungen informieren.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Solche\r\nÄnderungen haben nur für die Zukunft Auswirkungen auf die Beziehung zum Nutzer.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Mit\r\nder weiteren Nutzung des Dienstes akzeptiert der Nutzer die geänderten AGB.\r\nWollen die Nutzer nicht an die Änderungen gebunden sein, müssen sie die Nutzung\r\ndes Dienstes einstellen. Wenn die überarbeiteten Bedingungen nicht akzeptiert\r\nwerden, kann jede Partei den Vertrag kündigen.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Für\r\ndas Verhältnis vor der Annahme der Änderungen durch den Nutzer gilt die jeweils\r\ngültige Vorgängerversion der AGB. Der Nutzer kann jede frühere Version der AGB\r\nvom Anbieter erhalten.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:#444444;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Abtretung von Rechten und Pflichten<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\"\" neue\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:#666666;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\">Der\r\nAnbieter behält sich das Recht vor, unter Berücksichtigung der berechtigten\r\nInteressen des Nutzers alle Rechte und Pflichten aus diesen AGB zu übertragen,\r\nabzutreten, durch Novation zu ersetzen oder weiterzugeben.<br>\r\nDie Bestimmungen zu Änderungen der AGB gelten entsprechend.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"DE\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:\" helvetica=\